item.title: Privacy
item.description: Privacy Policy Welcome to DeepSketch (“DeepSketch,” “we,” “us” or “our”). DeepSketch provides a fast, beautiful way for you to sketch-like-stylize your photo. Just snap a photo, choose a filter to transform the look and feel, and share! Our Privacy Policy explains how we and some of the companies we work with collect, use, share and protect information in relation to our mobile services, web site, and any software provided on or in connection with DeepSketch services (collectively, the “Service”), and your choices about the collection and use of your information.

item.title: Introduction to DeepSketch
item.description: What is DeepSketch Sketches like art! We will make your picture a wonderful sketch. A nice sketch created by artificial intelligence Using the mobile-optimized artificial intelligence (Deep Learning) technology, you can create beautiful sketch artworks that look like people’s drawings. Select the desired picture and apply the sketch filter below to sketch the picture. You can save the sketch image or share it with an SNS such as an Instagram.

item.title: Contact
item.description: We are here to help you Are you curious about something? Do you have some kind of problem with our products? We do not yet have a service organization. Developers will review, identify and answer your questions and questions directly. Please feel free to contact us.
